WEBVTT

00:12.460 --> 00:15.160
[2012]

00:15.720 --> 00:18.760
[8/17 Case]

00:23.600 --> 00:24.280
Stop there! Freeze!

00:24.280 --> 00:25.030
Stop there!

00:25.800 --> 00:26.460
Stop there!

00:26.510 --> 00:26.920
Stop there!

00:26.920 --> 00:27.640
Stop there!

00:29.600 --> 00:30.320
Stop there!

00:32.520 --> 00:32.920
No, no, no.

00:32.920 --> 00:33.200
Don't move!

00:33.200 --> 00:33.600
Don't!

00:33.600 --> 00:35.220
This is my first time here.
I don't know anything!

00:35.220 --> 00:36.350
Please spare me this time.

00:36.350 --> 00:37.070
Zhao Ning?

00:37.560 --> 00:38.520
Why are you here?

00:38.790 --> 00:39.430
Brother.

00:39.790 --> 00:40.920
Brother! Save me, please!

00:40.920 --> 00:42.240
I'm scared. I don't know anything.

00:42.240 --> 00:43.000
Silence!

00:43.000 --> 00:44.060
Take them all away!

00:44.070 --> 00:44.530
Behave!

00:48.710 --> 00:50.430
Brother, save me. I'm scared.

00:51.640 --> 00:52.110
Go!

00:56.960 --> 00:58.560
Could you please help me plead

00:58.560 --> 00:59.620
with Captain Zhou?

01:00.150 --> 01:02.200
He's just a kid who graduated
from college not long ago.

01:02.200 --> 01:04.480
If he gets arrested,
his whole life will be ruined!

01:04.480 --> 01:06.150
He's the only son in his family.

01:06.150 --> 01:07.790
They're all counting on him
to be successful.

01:07.790 --> 01:09.850
What will they do if he gets arrested?

01:11.200 --> 01:12.760
L-Look, how about this?

01:12.950 --> 01:14.430
I... I'll release him secretly.

01:14.430 --> 01:15.680
Please pretend you see nothing.

01:15.680 --> 01:16.920
I'm begging you.

02:35.530 --> 02:41.150
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

02:41.500 --> 02:43.890
[Episode 20]

02:44.800 --> 02:45.400
On the day

02:46.400 --> 02:47.329
of the 8/17 Case,

02:48.310 --> 02:49.170
I was there too.

02:52.940 --> 02:54.130
I feel so guilty.

02:55.240 --> 02:56.770
Because of my selfishness,

02:57.630 --> 02:58.430
I've never had

02:58.430 --> 02:59.960
a day of peace ever since.

03:01.800 --> 03:02.860
Your selfishness?

03:04.000 --> 03:05.080
What is that?

03:05.960 --> 03:07.030
Come here and explain it to me.

03:07.030 --> 03:08.830
Don't come any closer, Zhou Jin!

03:09.250 --> 03:10.840
I beg you. Step back.

03:11.670 --> 03:12.730
Step back further!

03:17.800 --> 03:18.560
Stop asking

03:19.800 --> 03:21.960
and stop investigating, okay?

03:22.630 --> 03:24.430
The dead can't come back to life.

03:25.030 --> 03:27.890
Can you please just let go
of what happened to Chuan?

03:28.310 --> 03:30.710
Hengyun Logistics has been investigated.

03:30.800 --> 03:32.280
The drug factory has been seized.

03:32.280 --> 03:33.430
That's enough!

03:34.490 --> 03:36.960
Yao Weihai and Meng Junfeng
made a mistake.

03:37.030 --> 03:38.800
They shouldn't have tried
to get to the bottom of it.

03:38.800 --> 03:41.200
Why did they
have to mess with those people?

03:44.590 --> 03:46.240
I didn't do anything!

03:46.630 --> 03:48.960
I just passed on some information to them.

03:49.079 --> 03:50.800
I didn't go too far!

03:51.710 --> 03:53.240
It has nothing to do with me!

03:53.800 --> 03:54.870
Even without me,

03:55.280 --> 03:56.870
they would find someone else!

03:56.870 --> 03:59.200
Yao Weihai and the others would still die!

03:59.370 --> 04:01.020
They would still die!

04:02.240 --> 04:02.910
Zhao Ping.

04:05.080 --> 04:06.880
I just have one question for you.

04:08.080 --> 04:09.080
When those people

04:10.280 --> 04:12.080
tortured and killed my brother,

04:14.030 --> 04:15.160
were you there, too?

04:16.959 --> 04:17.959
What did you see?

04:19.589 --> 04:20.300
How did

04:21.560 --> 04:22.750
it happen?

04:24.280 --> 04:25.520
That's a whole different thing.

04:25.520 --> 04:26.980
Why on earth did my brother

04:29.610 --> 04:31.140
die such a miserable death?

04:33.980 --> 04:35.780
Zhou Jin, are you silly?

04:37.120 --> 04:38.500
Do you seriously still believe

04:38.500 --> 04:40.900
Chuan's death resulted from the 8/17 Case?

04:41.190 --> 04:42.800
That's just the surface!

04:45.600 --> 04:46.310
Who did it?

04:48.670 --> 04:49.520
Tell me.

04:51.420 --> 04:53.150
Who wanted to harm my brother?

05:00.480 --> 05:01.120
Zhou Jin.

05:04.390 --> 05:06.720
I will never let you know
in this lifetime.

05:08.640 --> 05:09.640
Why?

05:11.920 --> 05:13.180
Why would you say that?

05:15.120 --> 05:16.600
Why do you know so much?

05:17.870 --> 05:19.360
Were you also involved?

05:22.500 --> 05:24.300
How could I possibly hurt Chuan?

05:26.720 --> 05:28.040
In the whole SWAT team,

05:30.620 --> 05:32.620
Chuan was the one I admired the most.

05:33.950 --> 05:35.310
He was a good person.

05:37.720 --> 05:40.120
But what's the point
of being a good person?

05:41.940 --> 05:42.600
What a pity.

05:45.670 --> 05:46.520
What a pity.

05:48.190 --> 05:49.680
Don't come any closer!

05:49.870 --> 05:50.950
Stay back!

05:50.970 --> 05:52.360
I'm begging you!

05:53.110 --> 05:54.110
Move back.

05:55.520 --> 05:56.050
Back.

06:02.720 --> 06:03.310
Zhou Jin.

06:05.430 --> 06:07.160
You are just like your brother.

06:08.430 --> 06:09.890
You're as gentle as he was.

06:11.680 --> 06:12.280
Zhao Ping!

06:12.510 --> 06:14.560
Don't act rashly.

06:14.560 --> 06:15.400
Calm down!

06:15.430 --> 06:16.740
Don't do anything stupid!

06:16.740 --> 06:17.500
Calm down.

06:17.580 --> 06:18.440
Just calm down.

06:19.950 --> 06:20.880
Come back, okay?

06:21.310 --> 06:22.170
Come back here.

06:23.120 --> 06:23.920
Senior.

06:30.720 --> 06:32.520
I wanted to attend your wedding.

06:37.630 --> 06:38.600
Zhao Ping!

06:49.480 --> 06:50.110
Zhao Ping.

06:50.620 --> 06:51.250
Zhao Ping.

07:06.560 --> 07:07.270
Chief Tan,

07:07.890 --> 07:09.690
I've gotten out of Guangqi Bank.

07:10.000 --> 07:11.160
I've sent the backup to the team.

07:11.160 --> 07:12.760
I have the USB drives with me.

07:12.830 --> 07:14.960
Is there any footage of the deals in it?

07:14.980 --> 07:15.450
Yes,

07:15.630 --> 07:16.190
plenty.

07:16.630 --> 07:17.720
I think we can apply for an arrest warrant

07:17.720 --> 07:19.120
and catch them directly.

07:19.160 --> 07:20.240
Um, Chief Tan.

07:20.890 --> 07:22.550
How is everything on your end?

07:22.740 --> 07:24.000
Is it really Zhao Ping?

07:30.920 --> 07:31.560
Yes.

07:49.270 --> 07:50.070
Let's go back.

07:56.360 --> 07:58.310
Bai Yang and the others have already found

07:58.310 --> 07:59.310
those USB drives.

08:01.040 --> 08:03.900
It proves the high value
of Jiang Cheng's evidence.

08:04.510 --> 08:06.240
I will talk to the leaders again

08:06.530 --> 08:07.930
and make an application,

08:08.360 --> 08:11.220
trying to restore his identity
as soon as possible.

08:11.430 --> 08:13.490
Actually, the fingerprint on the gun

08:13.870 --> 08:15.000
can't convict him.

08:15.950 --> 08:17.480
Since we can't convict him,

08:17.890 --> 08:19.220
he can only be protected

08:19.390 --> 08:21.040
as an important witness

08:21.800 --> 08:24.130
instead of being identified as a suspect.

08:26.310 --> 08:27.270
Thank you, Sir.

08:30.040 --> 08:30.900
How about this?

08:31.830 --> 08:32.750
Later, I'll find someone

08:32.750 --> 08:34.750
to give you psychological counseling.

08:34.750 --> 08:35.880
Until we can confirm

08:36.590 --> 08:38.520
that you are in a good mental state,

08:39.409 --> 08:40.940
don't do fieldwork for now.

08:42.720 --> 08:44.030
I'm fine, Sir.

08:45.440 --> 08:46.370
Just do as I said.

09:17.910 --> 09:18.640
You're back.

09:27.480 --> 09:28.540
What are you doing?

09:30.030 --> 09:30.890
I'm exhausted.

09:33.870 --> 09:35.240
I need to recharge.

09:39.270 --> 09:40.130
Are you hungry?

09:41.910 --> 09:42.510
Yes.

09:43.870 --> 09:45.470
I'm craving instant noodles

09:47.000 --> 09:48.260
with a slice of cheese,

09:49.080 --> 09:49.960
luncheon meat,

09:51.240 --> 09:51.840
and an egg.

09:53.440 --> 09:55.040
And I want one more cold beer.

09:57.630 --> 09:58.030
Okay.

09:58.720 --> 09:59.580
I'll go make it.

10:08.630 --> 10:09.390
Today...

10:12.870 --> 10:14.330
we went to catch Zhao Ping.

10:20.720 --> 10:21.440
You knew it.

10:26.320 --> 10:27.320
Professor Jiang,

10:28.200 --> 10:29.400
I think it's time

10:29.750 --> 10:31.150
to root this person out.

10:31.780 --> 10:33.380
What do you think, Chief Tan?

10:33.410 --> 10:35.410
To catch a thief, you need evidence.

10:36.240 --> 10:37.790
Spread the news about the USB drives

10:37.790 --> 10:39.080
to the team.

10:39.670 --> 10:40.840
Say that the whole list

10:40.840 --> 10:42.370
of visitors is stored in it.

10:43.000 --> 10:43.930
Once knowing it,

10:44.320 --> 10:45.850
the mole will try to destroy

10:46.150 --> 10:48.150
the evidence before us by all means.

10:48.910 --> 10:49.970
I will send someone

10:50.600 --> 10:52.080
to monitor him the whole time.

10:52.080 --> 10:53.210
Once he makes a move,

10:53.910 --> 10:55.840
we'll make an arrest immediately.

10:57.150 --> 10:58.750
Chief Tan, you're calling me

10:59.150 --> 11:00.750
not because you don't have a plan,

11:00.750 --> 11:01.440
but because you are

11:01.440 --> 11:04.100
considering who should
carry out this mission.

11:05.080 --> 11:06.390
I find that I can't

11:06.800 --> 11:08.130
hide anything from you.

11:08.680 --> 11:10.210
Zhou Jin will do a great job.

11:12.270 --> 11:12.790
Okay.

11:13.750 --> 11:14.960
Hearing you say that,

11:15.510 --> 11:16.360
I'm relieved.

11:17.670 --> 11:18.200
Also,

11:19.600 --> 11:21.480
keep an eye on Jiang Cheng's safety

11:21.480 --> 11:22.910
in case someone tries to silence him.

11:22.910 --> 11:23.550
I got it.

11:24.000 --> 11:24.800
Rest assured.

11:25.630 --> 11:26.630
Professor Jiang,

11:27.550 --> 11:28.390
I think

11:29.910 --> 11:31.640
you are a very generous person.

11:32.550 --> 11:33.210
Good night.

11:39.440 --> 11:40.120
Zhao Ping.

11:43.550 --> 11:44.480
He died.

11:46.530 --> 11:47.290
He died?

11:52.450 --> 11:53.980
He didn't want to go to jail,

11:56.120 --> 11:57.780
so he jumped off the building.

12:00.670 --> 12:02.750
I wanted to catch him.

12:04.670 --> 12:06.200
But I didn't get the chance.

12:08.790 --> 12:09.920
It's not your fault.

12:13.440 --> 12:14.390
I should have

12:15.440 --> 12:16.910
gotten to know him better.

12:19.190 --> 12:20.950
We found out too late.

12:24.240 --> 12:25.500
But over the past year,

12:26.510 --> 12:28.630
I met him almost every day.

12:33.080 --> 12:34.480
Someone who wants to hide

12:35.120 --> 12:36.430
can hide very well.

12:38.600 --> 12:39.840
Was I so focused

12:39.840 --> 12:41.080
on my brother's case

12:45.000 --> 12:47.600
that I ignored the people
and things around me?

12:48.510 --> 12:49.750
Be it friends

12:51.360 --> 12:52.320
or family,

12:54.480 --> 12:56.160
I cared too little about them.

12:57.760 --> 13:00.090
How long has it
been since you called home?

13:00.140 --> 13:01.060
I forgot.

13:02.120 --> 13:03.910
But it was because I was afraid

13:04.510 --> 13:06.510
that they would ask what I was doing.

13:06.790 --> 13:07.920
I didn't want to lie.

13:11.550 --> 13:13.680
Let's go back and visit them in a while.

13:14.150 --> 13:15.150
I've been craving

13:15.570 --> 13:17.570
the waxberry wine your parents made

13:17.750 --> 13:19.210
the last time we went home.

13:26.670 --> 13:27.550
As soon as I got

13:27.550 --> 13:29.060
these USB drives from Guangqi Bank,

13:29.060 --> 13:30.720
I confirmed the contents

13:30.720 --> 13:32.150
with Jiang Cheng right away

13:32.150 --> 13:33.670
and did a technical appraisal.

13:33.670 --> 13:36.200
The contents inside
haven't been post-edited

13:36.200 --> 13:37.930
and are completely authentic.

13:38.100 --> 13:39.440
There are multiple videos
on the USB drives,

13:39.440 --> 13:41.320
involving several famous cases

13:41.480 --> 13:42.240
in Jingzhou,

13:42.600 --> 13:43.790
including human trafficking,

13:43.790 --> 13:45.960
smuggling, and drug trafficking.

13:46.510 --> 13:47.970
The solving of these cases

13:48.080 --> 13:50.550
more or less involved Comrade Yao Weihai.

13:51.120 --> 13:51.870
I believe

13:52.270 --> 13:53.480
that in this case,

13:53.900 --> 13:54.580
Cangfeng

13:54.840 --> 13:56.840
must have played a very crucial role

13:56.930 --> 13:59.530
in the process
of investigating the evidence.

13:59.750 --> 14:01.110
The whereabouts of Qi Yan and the others

14:01.110 --> 14:02.180
still remain unclear

14:02.180 --> 14:03.550
and under investigation.

14:03.550 --> 14:06.390
But according to the information
provided by Jiang Cheng,

14:06.390 --> 14:08.360
the Municipal Criminal Investigation Unit
and Nancheng Branch

14:08.360 --> 14:10.510
have both sent plenty of officers
to thoroughly investigate

14:10.510 --> 14:11.440
the persons

14:11.470 --> 14:13.640
and institutions
connected to Hengyun Logistics.

14:13.640 --> 14:15.900
I believe the results will come out soon.

14:16.070 --> 14:18.870
Comrade Yao Weihai realized
that his life might be

14:19.120 --> 14:21.380
in danger during the Jingang Operation,

14:21.720 --> 14:23.670
so he finally sent me

14:23.790 --> 14:25.150
a short message,

14:25.550 --> 14:28.790
handing over the phone numbers and a set

14:28.940 --> 14:30.540
of communication methods

14:30.910 --> 14:32.370
between him and Cangfeng.

14:32.390 --> 14:34.150
At first, it was Comrade Jiang Cheng

14:34.150 --> 14:35.960
who took the initiative to contact us.

14:35.960 --> 14:37.440
I couldn't confirm his identity

14:37.440 --> 14:38.840
as Cangfeng at that time.

14:39.000 --> 14:40.660
After consulting Director Lu

14:40.690 --> 14:42.330
and Professor Jiang,

14:42.360 --> 14:44.490
we conducted 2 tentative inspections

14:44.670 --> 14:45.840
on him.

14:46.390 --> 14:48.240
The tip-off was accurate

14:48.510 --> 14:49.440
and safe.

14:49.750 --> 14:51.150
That's why we carried out

14:51.480 --> 14:53.280
the Kuangshan operation later.

14:53.680 --> 14:56.200
In addition, before the Jingang operation,

14:56.480 --> 14:57.540
Comrade Yao Weihai

14:57.710 --> 15:00.160
gave me a small note,

15:00.360 --> 15:01.190
saying,

15:01.270 --> 15:04.360
"On October 3rd, at Jingang Wharf,

15:04.480 --> 15:05.410
make an arrest."

15:05.790 --> 15:07.190
And he told me personally

15:07.630 --> 15:09.870
that this intelligence came

15:11.000 --> 15:13.000
from the undercover agent Cangfeng.

15:13.000 --> 15:15.000
Later, we did a handwriting analysis,

15:15.000 --> 15:17.130
and it was Jiang Cheng's handwriting.

15:17.300 --> 15:19.030
Everyone, please look. This is

15:19.430 --> 15:21.690
the forensic report on the handwriting.

15:30.080 --> 15:32.750
In November 2012,

15:32.750 --> 15:35.080
I joined the Cangfeng Special Operation.

15:35.630 --> 15:37.960
At that time, Leader Yao found

15:37.960 --> 15:40.240
an illegal trading chain from the clue

15:40.240 --> 15:42.270
about the suspects of the 8/17 Case.

15:42.630 --> 15:44.480
To catch all the people
involved in this trading chain

15:44.480 --> 15:45.550
in one fell swoop,

15:45.840 --> 15:48.440
Leader Yao arranged for me
to start with He Wen,

15:49.150 --> 15:50.440
make contact with He Wu,

15:50.440 --> 15:52.240
and infiltrate the crime group.

15:52.270 --> 15:53.510
As I said before,

15:53.840 --> 15:55.300
it took us the whole 5 years

15:55.440 --> 15:58.100
to figure out
their organizational structure.

15:58.200 --> 15:59.260
This trading chain

15:59.550 --> 16:01.010
exists not only in Haizhou

16:01.360 --> 16:02.560
but also in Jingzhou.

16:03.180 --> 16:05.660
He Wu's in charge of the Haizhou area.

16:06.330 --> 16:08.400
And the criminal mastermind,
Old Scorpion, is the one

16:08.400 --> 16:11.400
actually holding sway
over the entire trading chain.

16:11.630 --> 16:13.240
The fingerprint on the murder weapon used

16:13.240 --> 16:15.800
to shoot Yao Weihai and Meng Junfeng
has been identified

16:15.800 --> 16:16.680
as yours.

16:17.360 --> 16:18.090
Jiang Cheng,

16:18.910 --> 16:20.120
we now require you

16:20.320 --> 16:22.120
to honestly state what happened

16:23.030 --> 16:24.690
after the Jingang Operation.

16:33.690 --> 16:35.890
I didn't go to Jingang Wharf that day.

16:36.600 --> 16:38.080
He Wu arranged for me to go

16:38.080 --> 16:39.880
to a warehouse on Jiangbei Road.

16:41.210 --> 16:42.410
How many people went?

16:42.840 --> 16:43.630
Two.

16:43.990 --> 16:45.630
Me and a young friend of mine.

16:46.720 --> 16:47.920
His name is Lei Dahua.

16:48.790 --> 16:50.150
Sirs, at this point,

16:50.150 --> 16:52.610
I'd like to add something
before I continue.

16:52.790 --> 16:54.870
This young friend of mine, Lei Dahua,

16:54.890 --> 16:56.910
has never directly participated

16:56.910 --> 16:58.140
in any criminal operations

16:58.140 --> 16:59.540
of Old Scorpion's group.

16:59.540 --> 17:01.810
And he covered for me to keep me safe

17:01.840 --> 17:04.000
in dangerous situations many times.

17:04.359 --> 17:06.359
So I hope you can be lenient

17:06.660 --> 17:07.500
with him.

17:10.200 --> 17:11.400
We'll discuss the situation

17:11.400 --> 17:13.470
you mentioned after the meeting.

17:14.880 --> 17:15.880
You may continue.

17:16.930 --> 17:19.260
After I arrived at the warehouse that day,

17:19.530 --> 17:22.460
there was an old guy named Qi
overseeing everything.

17:22.640 --> 17:23.880
At first, I thought

17:24.000 --> 17:25.160
he was Old Scorpion.

17:25.400 --> 17:28.000
At that time,
he was playing chess with Meng Junfeng.

17:28.000 --> 17:29.180
At the end of the game,

17:29.180 --> 17:30.970
he took out Yao's photo.

17:31.510 --> 17:33.040
Not until then did I realize

17:33.510 --> 17:34.780
that it was a trap.

17:35.270 --> 17:37.470
There was no so-called drug deal at all.

17:38.310 --> 17:39.270
They suspected there was

17:39.270 --> 17:40.930
an undercover cop among them.

17:41.270 --> 17:42.750
So they leaked this fake news

17:42.750 --> 17:45.200
to the newcomers who just joined them.

17:45.750 --> 17:47.210
These newcomers included

17:47.590 --> 17:48.740
Meng Junfeng and me.

17:53.410 --> 17:54.200
I quit.

17:55.200 --> 17:56.060
Are you scared?

17:56.630 --> 17:58.490
You even dare to catch the police.

17:59.350 --> 18:00.680
I've made it very clear.

18:01.570 --> 18:03.030
I'm here to make a fortune.

18:03.220 --> 18:05.080
I don't want to cause any trouble.

18:09.110 --> 18:09.870
Trouble?

18:13.160 --> 18:14.750
Do you know the 8.17 Case?

18:16.510 --> 18:17.720
Have you heard of it?

18:19.880 --> 18:21.270
I led the team to do it.

18:23.110 --> 18:25.710
But there's a detail
you certainly don't know.

18:27.030 --> 18:28.070
Yao Weihai

18:29.830 --> 18:32.160
killed someone he shouldn't have killed.

18:41.040 --> 18:41.810
Today,

18:42.870 --> 18:44.550
you can survive

18:47.240 --> 18:48.640
only if you kill him.

18:51.470 --> 18:53.600
It happened so suddenly

18:53.960 --> 18:55.920
that I really had no time and no way

18:55.920 --> 18:57.720
to inform Leader Yao of all this,

18:57.810 --> 19:00.210
and couldn't cancel the operation in time.

19:02.580 --> 19:03.620
You all know

19:03.960 --> 19:05.090
what happened next.

19:05.840 --> 19:07.250
They kept Yao Weihai under control.

19:07.250 --> 19:08.980
The police also found us there.

19:09.160 --> 19:11.360
They didn't care
about their underlings at all,

19:11.360 --> 19:14.160
pushing out some cannon fodder
to block the police

19:14.250 --> 19:16.850
and letting the major figures
evacuate first.

19:18.320 --> 19:20.320
Why did you act alone later?

19:23.560 --> 19:25.260
Because the police moved all of a sudden

19:25.260 --> 19:26.720
and caught them off guard.

19:27.040 --> 19:28.000
When pulling out,

19:28.000 --> 19:29.640
they didn't see their sniper,

19:29.640 --> 19:31.440
so they arranged for me to go to his aid.

19:31.440 --> 19:32.590
I only knew later

19:33.200 --> 19:33.830
that the sniper was

19:33.830 --> 19:35.440
their real boss.

19:36.270 --> 19:37.160
He is Qi Yan,

19:37.560 --> 19:39.190
the one we call Old Scorpion.

19:40.200 --> 19:41.520
What was the scene like

19:42.200 --> 19:43.600
when you first met Qi Yan?

19:45.090 --> 19:47.290
It was Zhou Jin from the Nancheng Branch

19:47.370 --> 19:48.000
who trapped him

19:48.000 --> 19:49.550
in an abandoned factory.

19:50.090 --> 19:51.860
Zhou Jin used to be my fiancée.

19:52.350 --> 19:53.720
Because of the special situation
at that time,

19:53.720 --> 19:55.640
I didn't tell her my identity.

19:57.000 --> 19:57.750
However,

19:57.920 --> 19:59.350
they caught Yao Weihai.

19:59.790 --> 20:00.680
I was afraid that my identity

20:00.680 --> 20:01.940
might also be exposed,

20:02.070 --> 20:03.930
so I had a few extra words with her.

20:04.200 --> 20:05.110
I thought,

20:05.870 --> 20:06.780
in case I died,

20:07.400 --> 20:09.440
she might understand what I was saying.

20:09.440 --> 20:10.500
Zhou Jin has already reported

20:10.500 --> 20:12.020
what you said to her.

20:12.510 --> 20:15.240
Please continue
with what happened afterwards.

20:26.640 --> 20:27.040
Cheng,

20:27.270 --> 20:28.000
are you okay?

20:39.240 --> 20:40.640
Did you clean up the tail?

20:41.160 --> 20:42.420
Isn't it enough that we saved you?

20:42.420 --> 20:43.480
Just cut the crap.

20:46.550 --> 20:47.810
Where is Old Scorpion?

20:50.880 --> 20:51.790
No rush.

20:52.660 --> 20:53.590
You will see him.

20:55.590 --> 20:56.160
How is it?

20:56.190 --> 20:57.050
Is the game fun?

20:58.920 --> 20:59.780
Pretty boring.

21:00.720 --> 21:01.750
Why not focus on making money

21:01.750 --> 21:04.150
instead of insisting on risking our lives?

21:08.790 --> 21:09.640
Jiang Cheng.

21:10.590 --> 21:12.190
You live too pragmatically.

21:13.560 --> 21:14.670
Sometimes,

21:15.310 --> 21:16.710
spiritual satisfaction

21:17.440 --> 21:19.440
matters more than material wealth.

21:20.680 --> 21:24.080
So your spiritual satisfaction is
killing police officers?

21:25.270 --> 21:26.670
What? Can't it be?

21:26.720 --> 21:28.240
I just enjoy it.

21:28.750 --> 21:29.920
Psychopath.

21:33.400 --> 21:34.190
Cheng!

21:34.680 --> 21:35.850
Mind your language.

21:35.880 --> 21:37.810
I can blow your mouth off, you know?

21:54.960 --> 21:56.760
You remind me of a friend of mine.

21:57.750 --> 21:59.280
A very interesting friend.

21:59.880 --> 22:01.410
He once called me that, too.

22:02.750 --> 22:04.310
"Psychopath."

22:06.590 --> 22:08.920
Do you know what happened
to him in the end?

22:10.040 --> 22:11.500
Did he also save your life?

22:19.000 --> 22:20.800
Jiang Cheng, you are quite cute.

22:22.920 --> 22:24.720
Thank you for saving me just now,

22:25.110 --> 22:25.840
Jiang Cheng.

22:27.360 --> 22:28.040
Xing,

22:28.920 --> 22:29.650
forgive him.

22:29.920 --> 22:30.930
Jiang Cheng is new here

22:30.930 --> 22:32.600
and not quite used to things here yet.

22:32.600 --> 22:33.600
Psychopath.

22:38.720 --> 22:39.350
Let's go.

22:39.840 --> 22:41.430
The game has just begun.

22:52.720 --> 22:53.350
Enough!

22:54.690 --> 22:56.020
Don't beat him to death.

23:12.750 --> 23:13.410
Leader Yao,

23:14.520 --> 23:16.120
hope you've been doing well.

23:19.590 --> 23:20.750
Qi Yan.

23:21.460 --> 23:22.830
It really is you.

23:23.440 --> 23:25.300
What did Jiang Hansheng tell you?

23:26.110 --> 23:27.070
Qi Yan is dead.

23:27.960 --> 23:29.130
I am not Qi Yan.

23:31.640 --> 23:33.200
I am here to avenge him.

23:33.910 --> 23:34.550
Come on.

23:36.240 --> 23:37.240
Let's have a talk.

23:38.240 --> 23:39.110
Back then,

23:39.350 --> 23:42.350
someone shot Qi Yan to death.

23:42.550 --> 23:43.370
Was it you

23:44.550 --> 23:45.830
or Jiang Hansheng?

23:48.960 --> 23:49.820
How about this?

23:50.810 --> 23:52.540
As long as you say it wasn't you,

23:53.640 --> 23:54.680
I will let you go.

23:55.640 --> 23:56.270
How's it?

24:00.030 --> 24:01.260
I fired the shot.

24:01.600 --> 24:02.320
No, no.

24:02.850 --> 24:03.350
Leader Yao,

24:03.350 --> 24:05.110
maybe you don't get me.

24:05.480 --> 24:08.400
I mean, as long as you say it wasn't you,

24:09.070 --> 24:10.830
and you had nothing to do with it,

24:10.830 --> 24:12.160
I'll let you go.

24:13.530 --> 24:14.480
It was me.

24:17.100 --> 24:19.560
Leader Yao, it wasn't you
who fired the shot,

24:19.620 --> 24:21.580
right? This is the truth.

24:22.400 --> 24:24.090
Jiang Hansheng did it,

24:24.960 --> 24:25.590
right?

24:26.110 --> 24:27.970
You only need to tell the truth.

24:28.740 --> 24:29.870
Come on, Leader Yao.

24:29.920 --> 24:30.950
Please!

24:42.140 --> 24:43.380
So boring.

24:46.880 --> 24:49.140
Since you don't want to make it out alive,

24:49.380 --> 24:50.770
play a game with me.

24:51.680 --> 24:52.400
Leader Yao,

24:53.350 --> 24:55.280
you've been tracking us for years,

24:55.750 --> 24:57.680
sending spies one after another.

24:58.310 --> 24:59.070
They came

24:59.960 --> 25:01.020
and died one by one.

25:05.720 --> 25:07.320
Don't you feel heartbroken?

25:08.070 --> 25:09.430
Of course, I understand.

25:09.430 --> 25:10.880
You are a cop.

25:11.640 --> 25:13.030
This is your duty.

25:13.920 --> 25:15.800
Then I hope you can understand

25:17.310 --> 25:18.710
that catching this spy is

25:19.630 --> 25:21.260
my duty.

25:22.550 --> 25:23.750
Now tell me.

25:25.000 --> 25:26.130
Who exactly is

25:27.230 --> 25:28.520
the spy you sent?

25:33.400 --> 25:34.130
You?

25:34.200 --> 25:35.960
Boss, Boss, it's not me.

25:36.500 --> 25:37.130
It's not me.

25:37.130 --> 25:37.850
You?

25:37.880 --> 25:38.360
Boss.

25:38.380 --> 25:40.180
Boss, please don't joke around.

25:41.350 --> 25:42.720
Boss, it's really not me.

25:42.720 --> 25:44.000
I really know nothing!

25:47.750 --> 25:48.400
You?

25:51.030 --> 25:52.160
Or...

25:54.920 --> 25:55.590
you?

25:58.750 --> 25:59.830
Before the deal,

26:00.160 --> 26:01.990
only these 5 guys knew about it.

26:02.720 --> 26:03.440
Leader Yao,

26:05.440 --> 26:06.680
point out the spy,

26:07.160 --> 26:09.160
and I'll make it quick for you, I promise.

26:09.160 --> 26:09.890
How about it?

26:10.240 --> 26:11.350
Leader Yao.

26:14.200 --> 26:15.800
It's fine if you don't say it.

26:16.590 --> 26:17.680
Killing 1 is the same

26:17.680 --> 26:18.910
as killing 5.

26:19.480 --> 26:20.880
I don't care.

26:21.470 --> 26:22.640
Say it!

26:22.720 --> 26:24.440
Say it! Say it now!

26:24.440 --> 26:26.440
You old thing,
are you going to get us killed?

26:26.440 --> 26:27.790
Hurry up and say it!

26:27.830 --> 26:29.270
Tell him!

26:29.270 --> 26:30.310
Enough!

26:30.330 --> 26:31.400
Stop yelling!

26:36.830 --> 26:38.490
Don't you two want to explain?

26:41.920 --> 26:43.980
Godfather, what on earth is going on?

26:45.490 --> 26:46.670
Jiang Cheng.

26:49.280 --> 26:51.740
Would you believe me
if I said I'm not the spy?

26:54.960 --> 26:57.760
Boss He, are you just going to watch
and do nothing?

27:05.090 --> 27:06.690
You're really a psychopath.

27:07.070 --> 27:08.870
If you want to kill me, just do it.

27:11.680 --> 27:12.310
All right,

27:12.530 --> 27:13.570
as you wish.

27:14.800 --> 27:15.600
Kill them all.

27:16.830 --> 27:17.540
Boss!

27:24.730 --> 27:26.340
Leader Yao, don't blame me.

27:26.370 --> 27:27.390
I don't want to die.

27:27.390 --> 27:28.450
I don't want to die.

27:28.550 --> 27:29.110
Xing,

27:29.270 --> 27:30.600
please don't shoot.

27:31.430 --> 27:33.690
Godfather! Godfather, I'm begging you.

27:33.730 --> 27:35.300
Please give me one last chance.

27:35.300 --> 27:36.160
I promise I'll serve you devotedly.

27:36.160 --> 27:37.130
I really misjudged you.

27:37.130 --> 27:38.690
Stand up!

27:38.720 --> 27:40.240
You are a cop!

27:40.580 --> 27:41.490
Cangfeng!

27:41.730 --> 27:43.050
Hold on to your faith!

27:43.270 --> 27:44.160
Don't be scared of them!

27:44.160 --> 27:45.720
Stop talking! Shut up!

27:46.560 --> 27:47.230
Godfather,

27:47.590 --> 27:48.930
please give me one last chance.

27:48.930 --> 27:50.350
I'm begging you, Godfather.

27:50.350 --> 27:51.590
I swear I'll serve you wholeheartedly.

27:51.590 --> 27:52.830
I don't want to die.

27:54.330 --> 27:54.990
Godfather,

27:55.500 --> 27:57.650
I beg you. Please give me one last chance.

27:57.650 --> 27:58.890
How come it's you?

27:59.570 --> 28:00.350
Sorry.

28:04.590 --> 28:06.630
I could tell from Yao's look

28:07.510 --> 28:10.110
that Meng Junfeng
exposed himself on purpose.

28:10.110 --> 28:12.090
He either knew about my existence

28:12.110 --> 28:13.910
or figured out

28:14.500 --> 28:16.020
I was also a spy sent by Yao.

28:18.030 --> 28:19.880
No wonder you kept making mistakes

28:19.880 --> 28:22.270
and giving me bad luck
for the past year and a half.

28:22.270 --> 28:23.960
So you are the mole.

28:26.240 --> 28:28.160
At that critical time,

28:28.750 --> 28:30.550
he was the one who stepped up

28:31.160 --> 28:32.430
and saved me.

28:40.350 --> 28:41.440
Sirs,

28:42.000 --> 28:43.460
I have finished my report.

28:43.590 --> 28:44.790
I didn't kill anyone.

28:46.350 --> 28:48.550
It was Old Scorpion who got them killed.

28:49.280 --> 28:50.720
The reason I'm alive is

28:51.550 --> 28:53.680
that Meng Junfeng took the fall for me.

28:54.750 --> 28:55.510
Jiang Cheng,

28:56.400 --> 28:58.530
what about the fingerprint on the gun?

28:59.480 --> 29:00.830
They gave me the gun

29:00.830 --> 29:02.870
and asked me to dispose of the bodies.

29:02.870 --> 29:05.270
The fingerprint was left on it
at that time.

29:05.750 --> 29:07.950
I could have wiped the fingerprint off.

29:08.000 --> 29:09.200
But I thought,

29:10.050 --> 29:12.310
since I had lost contact with the police,

29:12.900 --> 29:14.620
if the police could focus

29:14.650 --> 29:17.580
their attention on me again
due to this fingerprint,

29:17.640 --> 29:19.080
it might be a good thing.

29:21.160 --> 29:21.590
Okay,

29:22.000 --> 29:23.460
we have no more questions.

29:24.920 --> 29:26.120
After verification,

29:26.400 --> 29:27.110
the situation

29:27.110 --> 29:29.830
of Cangfeng operation
having double-line Investigators was

29:29.830 --> 29:32.190
filed as a confidential record

29:32.210 --> 29:34.720
in the Provincial Bureau
on November 21, 2012.

29:34.720 --> 29:36.120
This has been confirmed.

29:36.200 --> 29:37.350
Regarding the controversial parts

29:37.350 --> 29:38.750
in Cangfeng operation,

29:38.960 --> 29:39.920
particularly

29:40.480 --> 29:42.370
the questionable issues
in the series of activities

29:42.370 --> 29:43.370
at Jingang Wharf,

29:43.720 --> 29:45.720
this hearing has completed
the investigation,

29:45.720 --> 29:47.550
inquiry, and verification.

29:48.000 --> 29:50.070
After discussion and final ruling,

29:50.240 --> 29:52.720
the results of this hearing are
as follows.

29:54.830 --> 29:56.350
We fully affirm the contribution

29:56.350 --> 29:58.110
made by Comrade Jiang Cheng,
former Deputy Captain

29:58.110 --> 30:01.270
of the Criminal Investigation Brigade 2
of Fengzhou District, Haizhou City,

30:01.270 --> 30:03.720
in investigating the illegal trading chain

30:03.720 --> 30:04.810
in Jin-Hai.

30:05.440 --> 30:08.000
His suspected murder of Comrade Yao Weihai

30:08.400 --> 30:09.930
and Comrade Meng Junfeng is

30:11.030 --> 30:12.310
dismissed

30:12.910 --> 30:14.510
for insufficient evidence.

30:47.960 --> 30:48.690
Jiang Cheng!

30:48.760 --> 30:49.490
Jiang Cheng.

30:49.620 --> 30:50.440
Don't be in a hurry to leave.

30:50.440 --> 30:51.630
Wait here for a bit.

30:56.400 --> 30:58.730
What did you say? Someone is coming?

31:01.070 --> 31:02.800
Yes... Yes, someone is coming.

31:05.240 --> 31:06.100
Here she comes.

31:12.950 --> 31:14.450
A new police uniform is prepared for you.

31:14.450 --> 31:15.310
Go get changed.

31:19.080 --> 31:19.830
May I ask

31:19.830 --> 31:21.590
who prepared it for me?

31:22.200 --> 31:22.960
Chief Tan.

31:24.880 --> 31:25.310
Okay.

31:26.600 --> 31:27.640
Hurry up and get changed.

31:27.640 --> 31:29.440
Someone's waiting downstairs.

31:29.550 --> 31:31.010
Someone is waiting for me?

31:33.210 --> 31:33.600
Yeah,

31:33.630 --> 31:35.660
I should get changed first.

31:54.590 --> 31:55.070
Dad.

31:57.240 --> 31:57.750
Mom.

32:01.790 --> 32:02.350
I...

32:02.540 --> 32:03.390
I'm back.

32:24.710 --> 32:25.470
I'm sorry.

32:31.270 --> 32:32.800
It's good that you're back.

32:42.350 --> 32:43.950
You must have suffered a lot.

32:49.640 --> 32:50.160
Mom.

32:58.830 --> 32:59.880
I missed you.

33:08.130 --> 33:09.040
Cheng,

33:10.070 --> 33:11.480
why didn't you tell us

33:12.810 --> 33:14.940
before doing something so dangerous?

33:17.130 --> 33:19.610
Captain Tan told us everything.

33:21.890 --> 33:23.930
I didn't handle it well.

33:25.440 --> 33:26.400
You...

33:32.920 --> 33:33.980
What are you doing?

33:36.110 --> 33:37.370
None of your business.

33:37.980 --> 33:39.780
You came to see me empty-handed?

33:47.240 --> 33:49.280
Why didn't you just die out there?

33:49.790 --> 33:51.050
I was lucky to survive.

33:51.290 --> 33:52.480
How's your hot pot restaurant doing?

33:52.480 --> 33:53.550
Has it gone bankrupt?

33:53.550 --> 33:55.350
It became a chain a long time ago.

33:55.680 --> 33:57.010
Good thing you're back!

33:57.570 --> 33:58.440
Now,

33:58.660 --> 34:00.390
you can see how successful I am.

34:00.590 --> 34:01.240
Fine.

34:01.800 --> 34:03.530
You're doing pretty well, huh?

34:07.790 --> 34:08.480
Hey, bro.

34:08.500 --> 34:09.300
What's wrong?

34:09.800 --> 34:10.670
Don't put on an act.

34:10.670 --> 34:11.280
I'm fine.

34:12.800 --> 34:13.550
I'll live a long life.

34:13.550 --> 34:14.920
I'm waiting to inherit
your hot pot restaurant

34:14.920 --> 34:16.380
and enjoy a peaceful life.

34:17.409 --> 34:18.260
You?

34:19.510 --> 34:20.840
With your personality,

34:21.030 --> 34:22.090
you're like a fool.

34:22.880 --> 34:24.400
I'll outlive you.

34:27.880 --> 34:28.440
Cheng,

34:29.380 --> 34:30.380
welcome back!

34:38.290 --> 34:39.350
Alright, don't...

34:39.460 --> 34:40.719
Don't be sentimental.

34:40.840 --> 34:41.590
Stop it.

34:41.590 --> 34:43.389
I'll beat you if you keep this up.

34:43.770 --> 34:45.250
You want to beat me?

34:45.320 --> 34:46.030
You're getting cocky, huh?

34:46.030 --> 34:47.480
Come on.

34:48.320 --> 34:49.400
Come on.

35:15.840 --> 35:17.440
I'm relieved just to see you.

35:18.030 --> 35:20.030
-I'm actually doing fine.
-I know.

35:20.230 --> 35:20.960
Zhou!

35:22.710 --> 35:23.710
Welcome.

35:24.000 --> 35:24.710
Welcome.

35:24.730 --> 35:25.700
Thank you for your hard work.

35:25.700 --> 35:27.300
-Have a seat, please.
-Okay.

35:28.550 --> 35:29.760
We're truly sorry.

35:30.070 --> 35:31.550
Right now, the main culprits

35:31.550 --> 35:32.840
involved in this case

35:33.030 --> 35:34.440
still haven't been arrested.

35:34.440 --> 35:35.100
Currently,

35:35.360 --> 35:36.920
Jiang Cheng is a key witness,

35:36.920 --> 35:37.450
so

35:37.880 --> 35:39.880
he can't be completely free for now.

35:40.480 --> 35:40.840
Wait,

35:40.840 --> 35:43.240
we just want to have
a family meal together.

35:43.510 --> 35:44.880
Follow the leader's order.

35:44.880 --> 35:45.800
We understand.

35:46.760 --> 35:48.190
Seeing this kid safe and sound

35:48.190 --> 35:49.360
just puts our minds at ease.

35:49.360 --> 35:49.760
Yeah.

35:50.030 --> 35:51.710
We'll go see Zhou Jin later

35:52.030 --> 35:53.480
and then head back early.

35:54.860 --> 35:55.210
Good.

35:55.480 --> 35:56.110
Jin!

36:03.920 --> 36:04.630
Jin,

36:05.190 --> 36:06.240
look at Cheng.

36:06.440 --> 36:08.700
He looks best in a police uniform, right?

36:17.630 --> 36:18.320
Mom, Dad.

36:19.360 --> 36:21.490
Why didn't you tell me you were coming?

36:22.260 --> 36:24.920
We wanted to see Jiang Cheng
as soon as possible,

36:24.970 --> 36:27.050
so we asked Bin to drive us here.

36:27.140 --> 36:28.440
It's fine. We wanted you
to focus on your own work.

36:28.440 --> 36:29.600
Have you seen a doctor?

36:29.600 --> 36:31.000
Yes, it's nothing serious.

36:31.000 --> 36:31.710
This girl.

36:32.190 --> 36:32.840
All right.

36:33.070 --> 36:35.330
I'll leave you to chat with your parents.

36:36.320 --> 36:37.050
Jiang Cheng,

36:37.360 --> 36:38.560
come out for a moment.

36:55.390 --> 36:59.530
[Captain's Office]

36:58.760 --> 36:59.220
Come in.

37:02.760 --> 37:03.290
Sit down.

37:03.480 --> 37:03.880
Okay.

37:06.590 --> 37:07.440
Actually,

37:08.000 --> 37:09.460
there's nothing special.

37:10.320 --> 37:12.460
Since you are a key witness,

37:13.230 --> 37:14.360
the team has decided

37:14.590 --> 37:15.990
to arrange a dorm for you.

37:16.480 --> 37:17.210
In addition,

37:17.960 --> 37:19.160
we'll assign someone

37:19.670 --> 37:21.920
to specifically take care
of your daily needs.

37:21.920 --> 37:22.520
Thank you.

37:23.920 --> 37:24.980
In terms of safety,

37:25.230 --> 37:26.450
you need to be vigilant

37:26.450 --> 37:27.780
and careful on your own.

37:28.840 --> 37:29.920
Does being a witness mean

37:29.920 --> 37:31.300
I cannot be reinstated?

37:31.840 --> 37:33.550
You can't be reinstated for now.

37:33.550 --> 37:34.950
How long do I have to wait?

37:36.710 --> 37:37.910
Let me put it this way.

37:38.670 --> 37:40.470
About your identity as Cangfeng

37:40.550 --> 37:41.190
and

37:41.360 --> 37:43.490
your contributions to intelligence,

37:43.710 --> 37:44.510
I believe

37:44.760 --> 37:46.400
the higher-ups will highly value...

37:46.400 --> 37:47.730
I want to hear the "but."

37:50.880 --> 37:51.480
But

37:52.960 --> 37:54.960
you only had one contact person.

37:55.880 --> 37:57.540
Also, the only person who knew

37:57.630 --> 38:00.560
the details of your movements was
Leader Yao, right?

38:01.840 --> 38:02.440
Besides,

38:03.320 --> 38:04.880
you were in the crime syndicate

38:04.880 --> 38:06.070
for such a long time,

38:06.360 --> 38:07.690
got involved so deeply,

38:08.480 --> 38:10.140
and reached such a high level.

38:10.550 --> 38:11.410
Think about it.

38:11.960 --> 38:13.440
So the screening process

38:13.460 --> 38:15.320
will be relatively more complex.

38:15.400 --> 38:16.130
What's more,

38:16.550 --> 38:18.680
the fact that you took Lu Pengfei's gun

38:18.710 --> 38:20.070
must also be evaluated.

38:21.440 --> 38:22.970
The result may be different

38:23.960 --> 38:25.190
from what you expect.

38:33.760 --> 38:34.590
I get it.

38:35.840 --> 38:38.270
Some undercover cops turn bad
and become double agents,

38:38.270 --> 38:38.840
right?

38:40.440 --> 38:42.300
You could understand it that way.

38:42.390 --> 38:43.480
Don't take it personally.

38:43.480 --> 38:45.010
It's a standard procedure.

38:45.430 --> 38:46.290
Yes, standard.

38:46.410 --> 38:48.000
Here you are, the dorm key.

38:51.320 --> 38:52.250
I want to go home.

38:52.960 --> 38:54.360
Didn't I just tell you?

38:54.710 --> 38:55.760
You can't for now.

38:55.760 --> 38:57.360
Our case is still...

38:57.360 --> 38:57.960
Chief Tan,

38:58.590 --> 38:59.850
I won't leave Haizhou.

39:00.030 --> 39:01.840
I'll just go back to my old house.

39:01.860 --> 39:02.640
It's not far away.

39:02.640 --> 39:04.170
It's right in Jinze Garden.

39:05.710 --> 39:06.110
Okay.

39:07.190 --> 39:08.250
I can agree to that.

39:08.960 --> 39:11.160
As for the one assigned to look after me,

39:11.440 --> 39:12.570
I'd choose Zhou Jin.

39:13.800 --> 39:16.460
Don't worry,
I won't be too much trouble for her.

39:16.960 --> 39:19.160
Wait, do you think that's appropriate?

39:19.390 --> 39:21.250
You can ask for her opinion first.

39:28.440 --> 39:29.230
Jin,

39:30.230 --> 39:31.480
tell your man

39:32.290 --> 39:33.810
to drive over

39:34.110 --> 39:35.570
and take the goodies back.

39:35.840 --> 39:37.440
Last time I saw Hansheng,

39:37.590 --> 39:38.840
he seemed to like rice cakes,

39:38.840 --> 39:40.190
so I brought some extra.

39:40.630 --> 39:41.280
No problem.

39:41.280 --> 39:42.550
I drove today.

39:42.590 --> 39:44.050
I'll take them back later.

39:44.630 --> 39:45.960
Call him out for dinner.

39:46.150 --> 39:47.950
Okay, I'll call him.

40:02.550 --> 40:03.190
Hansheng?

40:06.840 --> 40:08.030
My parents are in Haizhou.

40:08.030 --> 40:10.090
Let's have dinner together tonight.

40:11.070 --> 40:13.800
My dad and Mrs. Fang
came back from abroad yesterday.

40:13.800 --> 40:16.330
I might need to have dinner
with them tonight.

40:17.480 --> 40:18.610
What a coincidence.

40:21.360 --> 40:22.280
All right then.

40:22.280 --> 40:23.810
Let's split up for tonight.

40:28.700 --> 40:30.300
Are you coming home tonight?

40:31.570 --> 40:32.780
Hard to say.

40:32.840 --> 40:33.860
I might be home

40:34.260 --> 40:35.220
a bit late.

40:38.310 --> 40:38.910
Okay.

40:56.580 --> 40:58.500
Is Hansheng tied up?

40:59.980 --> 41:00.820
It just so happens

41:00.820 --> 41:03.080
that his dad and Mrs. Fang are
back from abroad.

41:03.080 --> 41:04.880
They are having dinner tonight, too.

41:04.880 --> 41:06.000
Girl,

41:06.340 --> 41:07.400
you should have added

41:07.400 --> 41:08.740
that we could all have dinner together.

41:08.740 --> 41:09.740
We are all family.

41:13.670 --> 41:14.400
Sir,

41:15.260 --> 41:17.220
I'm not part of your family.

41:18.000 --> 41:19.110
We didn't mean that.

41:19.110 --> 41:20.630
Come on, I can tell it.

41:22.630 --> 41:23.360
Jin,

41:23.960 --> 41:25.150
you and Hansheng are

41:25.200 --> 41:26.730
not having a fight, are you?

41:27.760 --> 41:28.550
No.

41:28.840 --> 41:29.800
Why would we?

41:31.630 --> 41:32.190
Madam,

41:33.110 --> 41:34.200
if a couple

41:34.460 --> 41:35.460
never has a fight,

41:36.480 --> 41:37.550
that's even a bigger problem.

41:37.550 --> 41:38.760
Shut up.

41:38.780 --> 41:40.480
I didn't tell him you were here.

41:40.480 --> 41:41.320
If I did,

41:41.320 --> 41:42.720
there's no way he'd come.

41:43.510 --> 41:44.110
Sir.

41:45.060 --> 41:46.120
Your son-in-law is

41:46.300 --> 41:47.130
incredibly

41:47.440 --> 41:48.190
petty.

41:49.000 --> 41:49.850
Shut up.

41:49.880 --> 41:50.960
Stop holding my dad

41:50.960 --> 41:52.360
and badmouthing others.

41:53.630 --> 41:54.230
Jin.

41:55.360 --> 41:56.110
tell me.

41:56.710 --> 41:58.110
Does he know you once were

41:58.510 --> 41:59.840
engaged to Jiang Cheng?

42:02.090 --> 42:03.350
I told him everything.

42:03.540 --> 42:05.190
You are usually too busy with work,

42:05.190 --> 42:05.980
but

42:06.070 --> 42:08.270
you need to balance it with your family.

42:08.510 --> 42:09.360
You can't let

42:09.480 --> 42:11.610
Hansheng take care of you all the time.

42:13.190 --> 42:14.990
We're taking care of each other.

42:15.710 --> 42:16.360
Alright.

42:16.680 --> 42:17.400
Qiuyun,

42:17.840 --> 42:19.630
I think we should go back first.

42:20.000 --> 42:20.840
Go back?

42:21.400 --> 42:22.480
Not staying for dinner?

42:22.480 --> 42:23.410
Forget about it.

42:23.510 --> 42:24.760
It'll get dark if we stay for dinner.

42:24.760 --> 42:26.440
Bin will be tired from driving.

42:26.440 --> 42:27.500
I'm not tired, sir.

42:27.670 --> 42:28.270
Not tired.

42:29.630 --> 42:30.360
Zhou Jin.

42:30.840 --> 42:32.510
You should go home early today, too.

42:32.510 --> 42:34.170
His parents are back in China.

42:34.590 --> 42:35.440
You should

42:35.790 --> 42:37.390
visit them from time to time.

42:37.760 --> 42:38.710
Got it, Dad.

42:39.410 --> 42:40.110
By the way,

42:40.280 --> 42:42.210
do we still have any waxberry wine?

42:42.230 --> 42:43.880
Hansheng has been craving it.

42:43.880 --> 42:44.770
Yes, we do.

42:44.840 --> 42:46.280
Why didn't you tell me earlier?

42:46.280 --> 42:48.010
I could have brought some over.

42:48.280 --> 42:49.150
I forgot.

42:49.150 --> 42:50.780
And I didn't know you were coming today.

42:50.780 --> 42:51.380
It's fine.

42:51.390 --> 42:54.060
I'll bring him over to have some
when he goes back.

42:54.060 --> 42:54.870
I'm back.
